heme-excerpts\">\n                        <a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/themes/urban-bold/\"><h3>Urban Bold</h3></a>\n                        <p>Urban Bold is a a refreshingly simply blog theme with clean lines and makes great use of your imagery for a bold aesthetic. Urban Bold also offers some handy customization...</p>                    </div>\n                </div>\n                                            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\">\n                    <a href=\"/themes\" class=\"more-themes hvr-fade\">More Themes</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n\t<!-- Footer -->\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"footer-above\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div id=\"text-2\" class=\"footer-col col-md-4\"><h3>Shared Hosting</h3>\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\">There are loads of choices for shared hosting and just about any host who provides a basic linux based hosting plan will also offer one click installation of WordPress. However, if you are in the market for shared hosting our recommendation is to avoid the super cheap hosts and instead go with one of the bigger hosts. <a href=\"http://wpdevshed.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WP Dev Shed</a> have done a load of work reviewing hosts and monitoring performance so their recommendations are certainly a good place to start.</div>\n\t\t</div><div id=\"text-3\" class=\"footer-col col-md-4\"><h3>Managed Hosting</h3>\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\">If you are a business, or blogger, with decent and growing traffic then we recommend you considered a managed WordPress hosting provided. Again, there are many options, but our specific recommendation is Pressidium. Check out our <a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/pressidium-review/\">Pressidium review</a>. We use Pressidium and we have been very impressed with their performance and support. They are a new player, but they come from a long background in enterprise grade hosting and their platform reflects this.</div>\n\t\t</div>\t\t<div id=\"recent-posts-3\" class=\"footer-col col-md-4\">\t\t<h3>Recent Posts</h3>\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/six-essential-online-business-tools-for-freelancers/\">Six Essential Online\u00a0Business Tools for Freelancers</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/resources-for-studying-abroad-in-new-zealand/\">Resources for Studying Abroad in New Zealand</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/whats-the-difference-between-adsl-vdsl-and-fibre-internet/\">What\u2019s the Difference Between ADSL, VDSL and Fibre Internet?</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/responsive-photo-gallery-for-wordpress/\">Best Responsive Photo Gallery Plugins for WordPress</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://deucethemes.com/the-importance-of-good-project-management-for-small-web-shops/\">The Importance of Good Project Management for Small Web Shops</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\t\t                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer-below text-center\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n                        \n                        &copy; Deuce Themes \n                         \n                        - Powered by <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"static-link\">WordPress</a> \n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n\t\t<script type='text/javascript' src='http://deucethemes.com/wp-content/themes/deucethemes/js/bootstrap.min.js?ver=1.0.0'></script>\n<script type='text/javascript' src='http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-easing/1.